metadata.name: Jimmy Shoe
metadata.description:
Jimmy Shoe


Meet 32 year old Vijay .

His little corner stall opens at 10:30 am & shuts at 8:00 pm . The stall is just a corner on the footpath with a plastic mat and a loose thatch for when it rains . He sits all day repairing shoes on his anvil & fixes broken umbrellas too .

His hands laced with polish , his “om” tattoo almost disappearing under the polish, caught my attention.


Location : India 
Dimensions : 4902 x 3922
